    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being sold as a reliable daily driver that has seen some honest use. While it starts up reliably and handles well on the road, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few small door dings, and some paint fading on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and typical wear on the driver's seat. It is a solid choice for someone looking for functional transportation who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection.",
