      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated for the driver who demands both performance and sophistication. It exhibits a commendable level of maintenance, with all mechanical systems functioning to a high standard and an exterior that retains its refined character. Thoroughly inspected and prepared for immediate delivery, this offering represents a superb balance of luxury and long-term value.",
