      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my reliable daily driver and it's looking for a new home! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me. It runs great, looks lovely, and is totally ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a well-maintained ride that's ready to hit the road today, this is the one! Feel free to message me with any questions\u2014I'm happy to help!",
