    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit delivers linear torque through its six individual throttle bodies and is mated to a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis has been professionally addressed with subframe reinforcement plates to mitigate known torsional fatigue, and the S54\u2019s VANOS system has been overhauled with upgraded seals and a cryo-treated hub. Recent maintenance includes a precision valve adjustment and a fresh set of rod bearings for long-term reliability. The drivetrain utilizes the factory variable M differential lock for optimized corner-exit traction. While the exterior shows minor road-rash consistent with its mileage, the suspension geometry remains sharp with Bilstein B6 dampers and refreshed control arm bushings. This is a driver-spec example optimized for performance and mechanical longevity.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
