      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive condition both inside and out. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though you may find the occasional minor stone chip or light swirl mark consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the premium upholstery shows only soft creasing, and all electronics, from the infotainment suite to the dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, it is robust and road-ready. It boasts a comprehensive service history, including recent fluid changes and a full brake inspection. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts effortlessly, providing a comfortable and responsive driving experience. This is a reliable, high-performing car that perfectly balances luxury with everyday practicality, ideal for a driver who values a well-documented and well-preserved vehicle.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
